SUMMARY:MusikLab
DESCRIPTION:What is a MusikLab? \nWe provide the space and instruments and you do whatever moves you. MusikLabs are unstructured\, all ages (we recommend 6 months – 9 years)\, and all abilities.  \nVisit our website for details. Registration is required for each participant 17 years and under. Up to 2 grownups are welcome per registered participant. Please pre-register as spots are limited\, we recommend registering 24 hours or more in advance. $7 per child. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/musiklab-4/2026-03-16/
