SUMMARY:Mr Hoo Mondays @ SWPMA PLAY!
DESCRIPTION:Join us at SWPMA PLAY! in SW Hillsdale Town Center\, every third Monday for music time with popular local artist/musician\, Mr. Hoo! This padded play space is bright\, clean\, fully enclosed – and great for babes\, crawlers & little ones who love to boogie. \nChildren ages 0-5 are welcome. Ticket price includes 1 child and 1 adult. If you have more than 1 child\, and one is worn\, there is no extra charge for the worn child. If you have more than 1 child and they are ambulatory\, you must pay for each child please. *We work to pay our guest artists and instructors their asking rate/wage\, and this is how we are able to break even. If more $ is collected\, we pay the artist more. \n$12-$25 (Sliding Scale). Register and pay online\, or drop in and pay at the door: https://southwestportlandmartialarts.com/events/swpma-play/ \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/mr-hoo-mondays-swpma-play/2026-03-16/
LOCATION:SWPMA PLAY!\, 6315 SW Capitol Highway\, Portland\, 97239\, United States
CATEGORIES:Dance,Family Fun,Kids Calendar,Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Mr-Hoo-2026-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Southwest Portland Martial Arts":MAILTO:info@southwestportlandmartialarts.com
END:VEVENT
