SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Festival at Wonderlove
DESCRIPTION:A free\, multi-day\, all ages\, festival full of fun to celebrate Irish Culture at Wonderlove! Enjoy vendors\, live bands\, foodcarts\, and more! \n\n\n\n\nLucky You! You have stumbled upon Wonderlove for our annual St. Patricks Day celebration! \nSaturday\, March 14th: St Patricks Day Market \nAll ages\, free\, family friendly\, St. Patricks Day Market from 1:00PM-7:00PM! \nEnjoy the magical old world charm of our Irish market\, featuring local vendors\, 9 delicious foods to choose from\, specialty drinks (including a new Zero Proof Menu!)\, activities\, and more! \nLive Music from 5:00PM-7:00PM by Irish Folk Trio The Heartbleeders. \nSunday\, March 15th: St Patricks Day Market \nAll ages\, free\, family friendly\, St. Patricks Day Market from 1:00PM-7:00PM! \nEnjoy the magical old world charm of our Irish market\, featuring local vendors\, 9 delicious foods to choose from\, specialty drinks (including a new Zero Proof Menu!)\, activities\, and more! \nLive Music from 5:00PM-7:00PM by Traditional Irish Folk solo act Joseph Linahon. \nMonday\, March 16th: St Patricks Themed Trivia \nAll ages\, free to play\, chance to win prizes\, from 6:00PM-8:00PM \nSt. Patricks day themed trivia from 6PM-8PM. \nTuesday\, March 17th: St Patricks Day Finally \n21+\, free\, specialty themed drinks\, and Live Djs from 6:00PM-12:00AM \nTo end our St. Patrick’s day Festival we kick off the ultimate party with live DJs from 6:00PM-12:00AM! Catch Cazrep from 6:00PM-9:00PM\, and Shay Baca from 9:00PM-12:00AM. This is not a celebration to miss! \nAll events are free to attend! RSVP if you would like to be entered in for a chance to win daily prizes. \nLet us Eat\, Drink\, and be Irish. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/st-patricks-festival-at-wonderlove/2026-03-16/
LOCATION:WonderLove\, 262 SE MAIN ST.\, PORTLAND\, OR\, 97214\, United States
CATEGORIES:Family Fun,Festival,Kids Calendar,Music,St. Patrick's
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/St-Paddys-Day-Flyer-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="WonderLove":MAILTO:events@wonderlovepdx.com
END:VEVENT
