SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Day Storytime at UO Portland Library!
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, March 17\, for St. Patrick’s Day Storytime! There will be 2 storytime sessions\, one at 10:00 a.m. and one at 3:30 p.m. \nUniversity of Oregon Portland Children’s Library\, Second Floor\, Room 201 \nFree and open to our neighbors and the public! Free book borrowing\, of course! \nJoin School Psychology student Paula for fun and engaging storytimes\n— All are welcome! \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
